As per the decision taken in the meeting chaired by the Chief Minister,
The establishment of a health war room under the secretariat was under the consideration of the government.
The Government's Decisions:
As per the decision taken in the meeting chaired by the Hon'ble Chief Minister
Centre and State set up Health War Room under Chief Minister's Secretariat
All health-related to avoid the double benefits of government health-related schemes.
Integration of all health schemes in the state.
Toll-free number for assistance - 18001232211 to be used as a single number
Chief Economic Advisor to the Hon'ble Chief Minister and CEO, Mitra
The following Committee is being constituted under the Chairmanship of the Chief Minister's Secretariat.
